# Project Context
series: "Mission 100 by AI"
day: 2
category: full-stack
language: TypeScript
framework: Next.js 16 (App Router)

# Tech Stack
stack:
  frontend:
    - React 19
    - Next.js 16
    - Tailwind CSS 3
    - DaisyUI 4
    - Fabric.js 7 (canvas / hanko designer)
    - Chart.js 4 (dashboard analytics)
    - react-hook-form + zod (form validation)
    - next-intl (i18n — English & Japanese)
  backend:
    - Next.js API Routes
    - NextAuth.js (authentication + RBAC)
    - Prisma 5 (ORM)
    - Nodemailer (transactional email)
  database:
    - PostgreSQL 14
    - Redis (caching)
  storage:
    - AWS S3 (document & hanko storage)
  infrastructure:
    - Docker / Docker Compose

# Key Features
features:
  - Custom hanko stamp designer (canvas-based)
  - Document upload, signing & verification
  - Multi-step signing flow with approval chains
  - Role-based access control (Admin, Manager, Employee)
  - Bilingual UI (English / Japanese)
  - Dashboard with analytics
  - QR code verification for signed documents
  - Email notifications
